content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Security Agent Self-protection Trend Vision One Endpoint Security agent self-protection provides ways for the Trend Vision One Endpoint Security agent to protect the processes and other resources required to function properly. Trend Vision One Endpoint Security agent self-protection helps thwart attempts by programs or actual users to disable anti-malware protection.
